    <div class="main review-item" id="3110885">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3110885/" class="title-link">翻译得不好</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3110885"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/zct/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1009243-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zct/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">springfield</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-03-20"
      class="main-meta">2010-03-20 23:24:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3110885_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  翻译得实在太草率了吧，错误一堆一堆不说，连正文和注释提到的书名/人名都没有统一，这个是最起码的吧。 而且译者的汉语感觉似乎很有问题，好多句子那个“的”多得都数不过来。 好书不能烂翻！

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3110885/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
